node.text:
This Asian Pacific Islander Heritage Month, our API community is sharing how their heritage inspires their creativity. Hear @the.korean.vegan’s powerful reflections on her grandmother and share your work with the hashtag #OurDearElders for a chance to be featured.

"I’ve partnered with @adobe to honor #OurDearElders, and today, I honor my grandmother. My brave, ferocious, loving grandmother. Who slipped out of North Korea through swamp water and cut through the mountains on foot, all while keeping my father safe. Tell me, how do you honor your elders? How have their stories shaped you? What are some of the foods you like to eat in remembrance of those who came before you? Share how you honor them with #OurDearElders so that we can all join in on this beautiful discussion." - Joanne Molinaro
